modules.description: This module handles conversion and manipulation of strings encoded in Modified UTF-8, a format used by Java and similar systems. It supports operations like encoding from UTF-8 or UTF-16 sequences, decoding to UTF-8 byte strings, and inspecting string properties such as UTF-16 and Unicode lengths. Concrete use cases include parsing and generating Java class files, handling JNI string data, and working with network protocols that require Modified UTF-8 encoding.
